v26.3.15 update content:

Note: If you are currently in v26.3.2 version, you can update directly. If it is a previous version, you must uninstall and reinstall

update content:
1. Support the latest 1.30 series kernel, adapt to mihomo and singbox subscription client configuration
2. Support Anytls protocol, self-signed certificates or domain name certificates can be applied to Anytls
3. The 1.10 series kernel continues to retain all the original features, the 1.30 series kernel continues to be updated, and the two kernel modes can be seamlessly switched
4. Support local IP subscription link, menu options 3-8 can be set.

. For details, see: https://ygkkk.blogspot.com/2023/10/sing-box-yg.html
